{"tid":2105973,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參展書商用罷市迫令政府讓步有否干犯港區國安法??","createTime":"2020-07-13T04:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T05:41:28.000Z","uid":19552,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dcb5a15d1959251f5e8ff521a302882a16173276","tid":2105973,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"第二十二條 任何人組織、策劃、實施或者參與實施以下以武力、威脅使用武力或者其他非法手段旨在顛覆國家政權行為之一的，即屬犯罪：<br />\n<br />\n  （一）推翻、破壞中華人民共和國憲法所確立的中華人民共和國根本制度；<br />\n<br />\n  （二）推翻中華人民共和國中央政權機關或者香港特別行政區政權機關；<br />\n<br />\n  （三）嚴重干擾、阻撓、破壞中華人民共和國中央政權機關或者香港特別行政區政權機關依法履行職能；<br />\n<br />\n  （四）攻擊、破壞香港特別行政區政權機關履職場所及其設施，致使其無法正常履行職能。"},{"pid":"ee85bc95c294644badebbd61d3a240570404219e","tid":2105973,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"罷市係以極端手段威逼政府"},{"pid":"cb4d387d5f0a4cd8037a4f0dc59698375b42b661","tid":2105973,"uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"九巴係害群之馬"},{"pid":"a8932ec571df31b1789982ca1512ee090c032328","tid":2105973,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"證明埋政府已經失去管治能力"},{"pid":"d809f4f140b8b12eaa014d44abe73af4db0d5d32","tid":2105973,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:37:56.000Z","msg":"九巴黃到金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新鴻基原來係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a79f9942b7dd56996a8ba96f26dbf295da317c","tid":2105973,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ca75031de3c6d05a55571e69adb79c2c81b733","tid":2105973,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:38:03.000Z","msg":"支持拉哂果三間書商返去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c